                     <interp inst="t18201206-191-person1736" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a constable. About seven o'clock in the evening of the 8th of December I apprehended the prisoner at a lodging-house in Highgate, with this shirt, which was very wet. I asked him where he got it? he made no reply, but said he had been selling matches about Hampstead.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18201206-191-person1737">
