                     <interp inst="t18201206-191-person1737" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I keep the lodging-house. About two o'clock in the afternoon the prisoner came with this shirt; he said a gentleman at Hampstead gave it him.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. A man borrowed a shilling of me, and gave me the shirt till he paid me.</p>
